{"tid":2329568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國網民不滿遊戲《還願》上架　GOG數小時後宣佈下架","createTime":"2020-12-17T10:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T13:44:15.000Z","uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07ca77f68b2a4686a003b9d018efbe3c7a833000","tid":2329568,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/17/gog-devotion/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F17%2Fgog-devotion%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28XwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=dc29e6d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/17/gog-devotion/game-channel/</a><br />\n早前遊戲公司赤燭遊戲開發驚悚遊戲「還願」，但有玩家發現遊戲內有「習近平小熊維尼」字眼，隨即引起中國網友不滿，之後遊戲亦被下架。而遊戲公司赤燭遊戲近日就宣佈，「還願」遊戲會在 12 月 18 日於 GOG 遊戲平台重新上架，但是遊戲平台 GOG 就在宣佈後的幾小時，於 Twitter 宣佈，由於收到很多網民訊息，決定遊戲不會在 GOG 上架。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲平台 GOG 於 Twitter 宣佈，在今日稍早的時間，曾宣佈會重新上架遊戲「還願」，但是由於之後收到很多玩家的訊息，決定不會在其平台上架遊戲。據報導，GOG 是 CD Projekt 旗下的遊戲平台，有很多中國網友曾在 GOG 官方微博留言，會一同抵制遊戲《電馭叛客2077》（Cyberpubk2077）。有網友在 Twitter 留言，質疑 GOG 所稱的「很多玩家」是否指中國網民，另外亦有網友表示，對 GOG 的決定感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/TW-ONLINEGAME-XI_GbyEo_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FTW-ONLINEGAME-XI_GbyEo_1200x0.jpg&h=a014dc50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2cc02a9fd8fea82ce774790112d99650f2c84f7","tid":2329568,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fb3f2175d634ad32a1f446b2fe28185debd03f","tid":2329568,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"退錢2020"},{"pid":"d0dc3c7610efdea404cf376581670e128dc6786b","tid":2329568,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"呢隻絕對係一隻好game<br />\